Malipsdrift police outside Lebowakgomo in Limpopo have called on residents to help with information that could lead to the arrest of suspects and the identification of a person who was found burnt beyond recognition. The request came after the discovery of a burnt Mercedes-Benz Kompressor and a body burnt beyond recognition inside, in the bushes near the Leporogong village on Saturday. Spokesperson Motlafela Mojapelo said the police were not able to tell the nationality, age and race of the deceased at this stage as the body was burnt. “Anyone with information can contact Captain Matsobane Chwene on 082 414 3345 or alternatively call 086 001 0111 or SMS Crime Line on 32211.” -TNA Reporter